155.078 R-2 MANUFACTURED HOME DISTRICT.
(A) Purpose. The R-2 Manufactured Home District is established to provide for the orderly location and management of
low-density manufactured home residences on individual lots.

(C) Property development standards. Each site in the R-2 District shall be subject to the following property development
standards.
(1) Lot size. The minimum lot size for single-family dwelling units (manufactured or site-built) shall be 7,300 square feet.
llm_outputs.rationale: The section titled '155.078 R-2 MANUFACTURED HOME DISTRICT' provides the property development standards for the R-2 district, which includes the minimum lot size for single-family dwelling units.
